import './NavBar.css'
import { AppBar, Box, Toolbar, Typography, IconButton, Badge } from '@mui/material'
import { Facebook, Instagram, X, WatchLater, Email } from '@mui/icons-material'


function SocialMediaIcons() {
  return (
    <>
      <IconButton size="large" color="primary">
        <Badge>
          <Facebook />
        </Badge>
      </IconButton>
      <IconButton size="large" color="primary">
        <Badge>
          <Instagram />
        </Badge>
      </IconButton>
      <IconButton size="large" color="default">
        <Badge>
          <X />
        </Badge>
      </IconButton>
    </>
  )
}

export default function NavBar() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
      <AppBar position="static" sx={{ bgcolor: "#FFFFFF" }}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography
            className="NavBar"
            variant="h6"
            noWrap
            component="div"
            sx={{ flexGrow: 1, display: { xs: 'none', sm: 'block' } }}
          >
            <IconButton size="large" color="success">
              <Badge>
                <WatchLater />
              </Badge>
            </IconButton>
            Mon - Sat: 8am - 6pm
            <IconButton size="large" color="success">
              <Badge>
                <Email />
              </Badge>
            </IconButton>
            davidsgardeningservicesmedway@gmail.com
          </Typography>
          <SocialMediaIcons />
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </Box >
  )
}
